{"lastModified":1775127548290,"uri":"c::39480359087::vessel::e26fd690-ea32-11f0-ae84-3d6dcb8dc31a","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sicily, Italy, Sardinia, Malta, Calabria, Gulf of Naples\n\nFerretti 730 Fly is an amazing 23 meters motor yacht equipped with all the comforts for relaxing and comfortable cruises. Powered by twin 1420 hp MAN engines, it offers both speed and smooth cruising. Its spacious exterior includes a pleasant dining area on the aft deck, a large solarium on the foredeck and a wonderful fly bridge, featuring a second dining area, a large sundeck, the external helm station and a wet bar with barbecue. Inside, the Ferretti 730 Fly Angelica boasts a spacious and bright salon, with a lounge area and a dining room. It can comfortably accommodate up to 8 guests in 1 finely furnished master suite, 1 VIP suite and 2 double cabins, all with en-suite bathrooms and showers. All rooms feature a private bathroom with shower, a flat-screen TV and air conditioning. The yacht, in addition to being equipped with a washer and dryer, is also equipped with a 4m tender with a 50 horsepower Yamaha engine, equipment for water skiing, snorkeling and jet skiing.","blueprint":{"name":"FERRETTI 730 FLY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::e26fd690-ea32-11f0-ae84-3d6dcb8dc31a::assets::eb0c0d80-ea34-11f0-8450-81fa8014e4cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e26fd690-ea32-11f0-ae84-3d6dcb8dc31a::assets::eb131260-ea34-11f0-8450-81fa8014e4cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e26fd690-ea32-11f0-ae84-3d6dcb8dc31a::assets::eb150e30-ea34-11f0-bf1a-1f93f97cd2e1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e26fd690-ea32-11f0-ae84-3d6dcb8dc31a::assets::eb214330-ea34-11f0-8450-81fa8014e4cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e26fd690-ea32-11f0-ae84-3d6dcb8dc31a::assets::eb0b9850-ea34-11f0-8450-81fa8014e4cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e26fd690-ea32-11f0-ae84-3d6dcb8dc31a::assets::eb136080-ea34-